00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
High performers don't have more
willpower. They have better rhythms.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,000
You think you're lazy. Or undisciplined. You
try harder, push through, burn out.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:18,000
The most productive people work WITH their energy. Hard tasks in the
first 4 hours after waking. Admin and easy stuff in the dip.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Move your most important work to the first 3 hours
of your day. Don't fight your rhythm — use it.

5
